<H1>Marywood College</H1>

<H2>Business Affairs<BR>
</H2>

<P>
<HR></P>

<P><B>Vice-President for Business Affairs and Treasurer </B></P>

<P>Marywood College, a comprehensive Catholic College, seeks nominations
and applications for Vice-President for Business Affairs and Treasurer.
The Vice-President has responsibility for planning and directing business
and financial affairs, and most administrative services. Marywood has a
current budget of over $38 million and employs over 800. Advanced degree
in business, accounting, or financial management required; earned doctorate
preferred. Five years of experience at a senior administrative level such
as CFO required; experience in higher education preferred. </P>

<P>Screening will begin immediately and will continue until the position
is filled. Application materials include: current curriculum vitae; names,
addresses, and phone numbers of five references; and a statement of personal
philosophy (1000 words maximum) on fiscal and administrative management,
and should be sent to: </P>

<UL>
<P>Marywood College <BR>
c/o Search Committee VPBA <BR>
Office of the President <BR>
2300 Adams Avenue <BR>
Scranton, PA 18509 </P>
</UL>

<P>AA/EEO </P>

<P>
<HR></P>

