<h1>
<img src="Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt="IHM Web"><img 
src="Graphics/about_us.gif" alt=""></h1><br>
<h1>ABOUT US:<br>
Congregation of the Sisters, Servants of the Immaculate Heart of Mary, 
Scranton, Pennsylvania</h1> 
<img src="lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<br>
<h4>A hypermedia presentation that tells something of the story of the 
Scranton branch of the IHMs.  In the spirit of the 1995 celebration of 
the IHM Sesquicentennial Year, we celebrate the past, illuminate the 
present and attempt to get of glimpse of vision for the future.</h4>
<img src="lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P> 
