<DT><H3>18 /  Saturday</H3>
<DD><B>Connecting the Spiritual and Psychological Aspects of Our Lives to Gain a More Holy and Whole Perspective</B><BR>
The key to integrating the spiritual and psychological in our lives is discovering and discerning where connections occur.  This workshop will explore these practical connections in our everyday life.<BR>
Presenter:  Rev. Joseph F. Burke, SJ, M.Div., MA<BR>
9:45 a.m. - 3:00 p.m.<BR>
Center for Spiritual Development<BR>
Rye, NY<BR>

<img src="Lines/sb10-2.gif" 
