<DT><H3>25 /  Saturday</H3>
<DD><B>Ignatian Roots of Rahner's Theology</B><BR>
Drawing from St. Ignatius' experience of Trinity, Incarnation and the presence of the Holy Spirit in the soul, Rahner has tried to work on the interplay between the experience of the Christian person and the central mysteries of Christianity.<BR>
Presenter:  Rev. Gerard A. McCool, SJ, STL<BR>
9:45 a.m. - 2:00 p.m.<BR>
Center for Spiritual Development<BR>
Rye, NY<BR>

