<DD><B>Embracing Our Experiences</B><BR>
This full day conference for women and men religious will address the sensitive areas of our relationship with ourselves, the intimacy needs that must be addressed as well as those we have yet to identify and how community life as it is presently experienced can help or hinder the depths we reach in loving ourselves as God loves us.<BR>
Presenter:  Donald Bisson, FMS<BR>
9:00 a.m. - 4:00 p.m.<BR>
