<DT><H3>2 - 4 / Friday - Sunday</H3>
<DD><B>Fertile Fields</B><BR>
A grassroots, intercongregational gathering of women religious under the age of 50.  <I>Fertile Fields</I> will offer an opportunity for women religious to examine the theological, psychological and sociological contexts that have shaped their religious journey; to share stories of faith and struggle, to find reason to hope and dream at this moment in history.  The weekend will include input by Sr. Mary Johnson SNDdeN; Sr. Judy Eby, RSM; and Sr. Roban Kubic, SC.<BR>
Cost:  $150.00<BR>
St. Joseph Center<BR>
Greensburg, PA<BR>
For further information, contact Sr. Catherine Luxner<BR>


