<head>
<title>IHM Web:  Claim to Fame</title>
</head>
<body>
<h2>
<img src="Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt="IHM Web:  Our Claim to Fame"></h2><br>
<P>
Established on June 12, 1995, the IHM Web Home Page has the privilege to 
be the first site created by a women's religious order.  Those sites in 
existence prior to IHM Web were either orders of men or composite groups.
<P>
We are excited at the possibilities this medium provides for us as we 
investigate the ways it will allow us to present our identity to the 
world, work to further our mission and facilitate communication with and 
among our membership.
<P>
<img src="Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
<a href="index.html">Return to the IHM Web Home Page</a>
