12 semester hours <br>
*EDUC 471 The First Five Years, Part I	3 <br>
*EDUC 472 The First Five Years, Part II	3 <br>
*EDUC 506 Problems and Issues in Early Childhood Education 	3 <br>
*EDUC 509 Administration, Organization and Supervision of ECE Programs 
	3 <p>
