Other courses may be selected with approval of the Chairperson. 
In addition to demonstrated competency in the core and concentration  
courses listed, an Instructional I candidate needs to complete: <p>

*EDUC 000 Field Experience, Section 09 	0 <br>
*EDUC 442 Student Teaching 	12 <br>
