<center><B>MARYWOOD SNOWLINE</B> </center>
<P>
<B>Call the Marywood SNOWLINE, 961-4SNO, for updated closing,
cancellation &amp; delay announcements for Marywood College.</B>
Information will also be given to most local TV &amp; radio stations.
Classes will be delayed or canceled if significant snow accumulations
occur. Other weather problems will be dealt with as determined
prudent. Students are advised to use their own discretion regarding
travel to the campus.
<P>
<center><B>TODAY'S MEETINGS</B> </center>
<P>
<B>Communication Arts majors Department meeting</B>, 2 p.m., PAC
Auditorium. Please attend or a Practicum deduction may be issued.
<P>
<center><B>UPCOMING MEETINGS</B> </center>
<P>
<B>Multi-Cultural Club meeting</B>, 11/14, 9 p.m., Lynett Board
Room, Nazareth Student Center.
<P>
