Volunteers Office, Regina Hall, 348-6211.
<P>
<B>The Dr. John H. Corcoran Scholarship is awarded by The Friendly
Sons Of Saint Patrick Of Lackawanna County. This $3,000 scholarship
is intended to</B> support study at an Irish university for the
'97 Summer or the following semester. Applicants must have a minimum
Grade Point Average of 3.0 &amp; preference will be given to students
from Lackawanna County. If you are interested in competing for
this scholarship, contact Dr. Peter Spader, immediately, in LAC
120 or call 348-6211, ext. 2576.
