alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
Reference
<P>
Gannon, Margaret (Ed.) (1992).  Paths of Daring, Deeds of Hope:  Letters 
by and about Mother Theresa Maxis Duchemin.  Scranton, PA:  Congregation 
of the Sisters, Servants of the Immaculate Heart of Mary, Monroe, MI and 
Scranton, PA
