<h2>
<img src="../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt=""><img 
src="../Graphics/b_w_fame.gif" alt="Brushes With Fame"></h2><br>
This is a presentation listing famous and influential people who have 
ties with the Sisters of IHM of Scranton, PA.
<P>
<h3>|<a href="#politicians">Politicians</a>|<a href="#sports">Sports 
Figures</a>|<a href="#entertainers">Entertainers</a>|<a 
href="#church">Church Notables</a>|<a href="#other">Other</a>|</h3>
