<html>
<head>
<title>IHM Web:  About Us:  IHM Present:  Where We Are</title>
</head>
<body>
<h2>
<img src="../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt="IHM Web:  About Us:  "><img 
src="../Graphics/where_are.gif" alt="Where We Are"></h2>
The purpose of this presentation is to give you a look at where Scranton 
IHMs are currently serving and the ministries they are involved in.  To 
see where we have served in the past, check out the <a 
href="where-been.html">Where We've Been</a> presentation listed under IHM 
Past in the <a href="../about-us.html">About Us Menu</a>.
<P>
<img src="../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
<a name="world"><h3>Select a country:</h3></a>
<P>
<h3>| <a href="#canada">Canada</a> | <a 
href="#guatemala">Guatemala</a> | 
<a href="#israel">Israel</a> | <a href="#peru">Peru</a> | <a 
href="#usa">USA</a> |</h3>
<P>
<img src="../Lines/sb10.gif" 
alt= 
" ____________________________________________________________________
