<html>
<head>
<title>IHM Web:  About Us:  IHM Present:  What We Do</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>
<img src="../../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt=""><img 
src="../../Graphics/what_do.gif" alt="What We Do"></h1> 
<P>
In this presentation, five Scranton IHM sisters describe daily life as they 
live it ... in the streets of New York City,  a classroom in Scranton, a 
clinic in Silver Spring, a Riverside, MD parish and the Andes Mountains in 
Peru.  These articles were originally published in the Winer 1995 
edition of <strong>Journey</strong>, the ministry publication of the 
Scranton IHM Congregation.
<P>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
<dl>
<dt><a href="helene.html"><img src="../../Graphics/cyancube.gif" alt="*"> 
Sr. Helene Hicks</a> 
<dd>nurse at the Catholic Spanish Center in Silver Spring, MD
<P>
<dt><a href="mary_n.html"><img src="../../Graphics/cyancube.gif" alt="*"> 
Sr. Mary Newett</a>
<dd>pastoral associate in Riverside, MD
<P>
<dt><a href="eliza.html"><img src="../../Graphics/cyancube.gif" 
alt="*"> Sr. Elizabeth Muir</a>
<dd>first grade teacher in a Catholic school in Scranton, PA
<P>
<dt><a href="nancy.html"><img src="../../Graphics/cyancube.gif" alt="*"> Sr. 
Nancy DeCesare</a>
<dd>Director of Social Services at New York Foundling Hospital
<P>
<dt><a href="mary_e.html"><img src="../../Graphics/cyancube.gif" alt="*"> 
Sr. Mary Elaine Anderson</a>
<dd>pastoral minister in San Felipe, Sicuani, Peru
<P>
</dl>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
