<h2>
<img src="../../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt=""><img 
src="../../Graphics/could_be.gif" alt="It Could Be You!"></h2><br>
<h3>"In my Father's house are many mansions..."</h3>

There are many types of membership or association in the IHM Family.  We 
invite you to explore the descriptions of each of the following, bearing 
in mind that <em>this could be you!</em>
