<title>IHM Calendar:  Guest House Workshops</title>
</head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<a name="top"></a>
<CENTER><h1>
<img src="../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt="IHM Web"><img 
src="../Graphics/calendar.gif" alt="IHM Calendar of Events"></h1></CENTER><br>
<center>
<h2>Guest House Workshops</h2>
<H3>Free One-Day Presentations</H3></center>
<I>Since 1994, Guest House is dedicated to caring for Catholic Sisters and women in religious formation suffering from alcoholism, other chemical dependencies and related problems</I>

<P>
<H3>Topics</H3>

<TABLE  CELLSPACING=2 CELLPADDING=1>
<TR>
	<TD><UL>
		<LI>Addiction and Religious Formation
		<LI>Eating Disorders
		<LI>Gambling & Excessive Spending
		<LI>Over the Counter Drug Dependency
		<LI>The Insulation of Isolation
	</UL>


	<TD>
	<UL>
		<LI>Multiple Medications
		<LI>The Many Faces of Addiction
		<LI>Sexual Issues
		<LI>Work and Ministry
		<LI>Addiction and the Older Sister
	</UL>

</TABLE>
<P>
<H3>Schedule</H3>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
8:30 a.m. -- Breakfast and Registration<BR>
9:30 a.m. - 3:30 p.m. -- Program
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>
<H3>Locations and Dates</H3>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
	Catholic University<BR>
	Washington, DC<BR>
	February 4, 1997
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
	Cenacle Retreat House<BR>
	Rockville Center, NY<BR>
	March 6, 1997
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
	Mother Boniface Center<BR>
	Philadelphia, PA<BR>
	April 8, 1997
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<P>
<H3>Registration Contact:</H3>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
	Guest House<BR>
	P.O. Box 420<BR>
	Lake Orion, MI  48361<BR>
	800-626-6910
</BLOCKQUOTE>
