<DOCOLDNO>IA089-000959-B006-93</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://marywood1.marywood.edu:80/www2/ihmpage/About-us/What-do/nancy.html 192.159.104.1 19970110052436 text/html 7246
HTTP/1.0 200 Sending document
