<title>IHM Web:  About Us:  IHM Future:  It Could Be You:  Friends</title>
</head>
<body>
<h2>
<img src="../../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt=""><img 
src="../../Graphics/could_be.gif" alt="It Could Be You!"></h2><br>
<h2>IHM Friends</h2>
The Congregation of the Sisters, Servants of the Immaculate Heart of 
Mary enjoys the benefits of association with our many friends -- those 
of the Congregation at large, of local communities and of our individual 
members.
<P>
Our friends bless us with their prayers, presence and support.  Their 
contributions to the life and mission of the Scranton IHMs are important 
and appreciated.  We often invite them to share with us in our 
celebrations and at other community events.  We remember their 
intentions in our personal and community prayers.
<P>
