<h2>IHM Benefactors</h2>
Our benefactors give us financial and/or material contributions.  These 
may be given to the Congregation, to a local community, or to individual 
members.  We express our thanks to our benefactors in many ways including 
daily remembrance in our prayers and in a monthly liturgy.
<P>
The IHM Development Office coordinates a number of formalized programs 
for those who wish to help with the temporal needs of the Congregation.  
Select a title below to learn more about that area:
