<body>
<h2>
<img src="../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt="IHM Web:  "><img 
src="../Graphics/cresco.gif" alt="Spiritual Renewal Center"></h2><br>
<h2>Hermitage Retreats</h2> 
Two hermitages in the Pocono Mountains of northeast Pennsylvania are 
available all year for retreats.
<P> 
Cost:  $25.00 per day, $20.00 for Religious
<P> 
For information or brochure, contact
<pre>
         IHM Spiritual Renewal Center
         Box 568, RR 1
         Cresco, PA  18326
 
         717-595-7548
</pre> 
<img src="../../lines-dir/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
For hermitages located on the IHM property in Scranton, PA, call 717-342-6850
<P>
<img src="../../lines-dir/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
The IHM Spiritual Renewal Center is located in a peaceful setting in the 
heart of the Pocono Mountains of northeast Pennsylvania.  Private and 
directed retreats are also available.  The Center has accomodations for 
groups of up to 15 overnight guests and can accomodate up to 35 for a day 
program.
<P>
<img src="../../lines-dir/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
