                  Style - Psychadelic, weird ambiance (4:20- blocks
                          from another universe)<Br>
<HR>
<P>As you can see, VMFM offers a lot of programming time with a lot of variety
during the day.  If you're tired of the same old, dull, boring, sissy Top 40
stations, you should come and check us out.  We're just left of Oldies 92 on your dial at 91.5 in the Scranton/Wilkes-Barre listening area.  If you're not within
our listening area, and would still like to keep up with VMFM, send a message
to: <B>Commarts@ac.marywood.edu</B><Br>
In the SUBJECT heading, type "VMFM" and in the body of the message type
"Subscribe (YOUR USER NAME@your email address).  Everytime this list is
updated, you will automatically recieve a newsletter with a list of our
current "Hot List", any programming changes, as well as any upcoming special
programs on WVMW-FM.  

