<Title>Pacer Pride</Title>
<body background="images/backgrnd.gif">
<Center><H1>Pacer Pride: Your source for Marywood Sports</H1></Center>
</HEAD>
<Body>
<HR>
<P> So, you want all the inside stuff??  The stats, the scores, who's hot and
who's not???  Welcome to Pacer Pride, the Marywood College Sports Information
Show.  This show is the public's access to stuff that you may not see in the
papers.  Your hosts, Bill Jones and John Seitzinger, give you the low-down on
what's going down with all of Marywood's sports.  Broadcast on VMFM 91.5 every
Tuesday from 12pm-1pm and shown on TVM-37 every Tuesday and Thursday at 7:30pm,
it is THE show for sports junkies.  Bill Jones, the insider, talks about what
is going on off the field and on it, while "The Coach" John Seitzinger, has
stats and interviews with all of the stars here at Marywood.  If you want the
inside skinny on the Pacers, tune into Pacer Pride on VMFM 91.5, and TVM-37.
