<B>A Closer Look</B><BR>
"A Closer Look" is TVM-37's newest show and also is a classroom exercise in 
producing, crewing, directing, creating news packages, and just about
everything else that goes into creating a news program. Done in a news magazine
format, "A Closer Look" is cable-cast every other week. During the off week, A
Closer Look does a radio newscast that is aired on WVMW-FM,91.5,  Marywood's
 radio station.   
