<body>
<h2>
<img src="../../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt="IHM Web:  About Us:  "><img 
src="../../Graphics/could_be.gif" alt="It Could Be You!"></h2><br>
<h2>IHM Special Funds</h2>
Persons wishing to donate money to the IHM Congregation may stipulate 
its distribution to the following funds:
<P>
<dl>
<dt>IHM Retirement Fund
<dd>The IHM Charitable Trust for future retirement needs
<P>
<dt>Marian Convent
<dd>For the present care of our retired members
<P>
<dt>Operating Fund
<dd>General support of all IHM ministries.  Funds are used to meet the 
greatest needs at any given time.
<P>
<dt>Theresa's Treasure
<dd>Seed money for women's projects and the poor
<P>
<dt>Foreign Missions
<dd>Supports the work of IHM sisters in Peru
<P>
<dt>Guatemala Fund
<dd>Restricted to the support of Sr. Donna Korba's ministry in Guatemala
<P>
</dl>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
For more information about these funds, or to make a contribution, contact:
<P>
<pre>
		Director of Development
		IHM Center
		2300 Adams Avenue
		Scranton, PA  18509

		(717-346-5431)
</pre>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
