<body>
<h2>
<img src="../../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt="IHM Web:  About Us:  "><img 
src="../../Graphics/could_be.gif" alt="It Could Be You!"></h2><br>
<h2>Silver Circle Membership Program</h2>
<dl>
<d>What is it?  
<dd>A fund raising program in support of the IHM Retirement Fund
<P>
<dt>How much does it cost?  
<dd>$25.00 for each membership.  You may purchase as many as you choose.
<P>
<dt>Why should I join?  
<dd>You will have 296 chances to win prizes -- $50.00 at 
the lowest and $1,000 at the highest.  Drawings are held each month, 
October - June, at the Marian Convent, Scranton, PA.
<P>
<dt>What are the other benefits?  
<dd>You will share in the daily prayers and works of our IHM Sisters.  
You will also be remembered at the monthly mass for our benefactors.
<P>
Your membership(s) will help us to continue caring for the sick and 
aging Sisters of the IHM Congregation.
<P>
</dl>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
For further information, or to join the program, contact:
<P>
<pre>
          Director of Development
          IHM Center
          2300 Adams Avenue
          Scranton, PA  18509

	  (717-346-5431)
</pre>
