<body>
<h2>
<img src="../../Graphics/ihmlogo3.gif" alt="IHM Web:  About Us:  "><img 
src="../../Graphics/could_be.gif" alt="It Could Be You!"></h2><br>
<h2>Memorial and Honorary Greeting Cards</h2>
The IHM Development Office provides memorial and honorary greeting cards 
for those who wish to make a gift "in honor of" or "in memory of" a loved one.
<P>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
<a href="../../Graphics/honor.gif"><img src="../../Graphics/honor-th.gif" 
alt="[Picture of the card]"> The Honorary Card</a> is appropriate for many 
occasions including feast days, birthdays, weddings, anniversaries, 
graduations, first communions, confirmations, etc.
<P>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
<a href="../../Graphics/birthday.gif"><img 
src="../../Graphics/birthday-th.gif"
alt="[Picture of the card]"> The Birthday Card</a> is a unique 
way  to remember the birthday of someone special.
<P>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif"
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
<a 
href="../../Graphics/memorial.gif"><img 
src="../../Graphics/memorial-th.gif" alt="[Picture of the card]"> 
<a
href="../../Graphics/memorial2.gif"><img
src="../../Graphics/memorial2-th.gif" alt="[Picture of the card]">
A Memorial Card</a> will bring a special message of comfort to families 
upon the loss of a loved one.  Two versions are available.
<P> 
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
<a href="../../Graphics/insert.gif"><img src="../../Graphics/insert-th.gif" 
alt="[Picture of the card]"> The Insert Card</a> can be placed inside any 
greeting card.  This card tells the recipient that a donation has been 
made in his/her honor to Theresa's Treasure. 
<P>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
<P>
These cards may be acquired from the IHM Development Office.  Each card 
will contain a remittance envelope addressed to the Development Office.  
Upon sending the card, fill out the information on the remittance 
envelope, enclose your gift and mail to the Development Office.  You 
will promptly receive a thank you letter and a replacement card.
<P>
<pre>
		Director of Development
		IHM Center
		2300 Adams Avenue
		Scranton, PA  18509

		(717-346-5431)
</pre>
<img src="../../Lines/sb10-1.gif" 
alt="____________________________________________________________________">
