<Title>Nick Taylor</Title>
<body background="/images/backgrnd.gif">
<Center><H1>Nick's Page</H1></Center>
</Head>
<Body>
<P> So you clicked on me, Nicky T.  Well, this isn't a personal page or
anything like that, so if you want to know more about me, your going to have to
be a bit more resourceful.  Nice try though.  This page is my own personal
page of what I is going on at the station. Watch this space for news.<Br>

<P><Center><B>Live in the studio!!!!!  Dick Fawcett</B></Center><Br>

Next Monday, April 8th 1996, local band Dick Fawcett will be live in the studio
with me, Nicky T. Starting at 10pm, Scranton's premier all-original band will
be in the studio playing songs that they wrote, as well as a Q & A with me. 
Think of it as a live concert for free!  It should be a very entertaining
evening, so be sure to tune in.  That's Monday April 8th, 1996.  <Br>

<P>Well, that's it for this month.  Listen to VMFM or I'll come to your house
and kill you!!!  Ok, well maybe I'll just feel insulted.<Br>
					      <P>-Nick<Br>

This file last updated <B>April 2, 1996</B><Br>
Copyright 1996.  All rights reserved.
 
