<HTML>
<body background="/images/background.gif">
<B>Guitar Shop</B><BR> 
Join Charlie Russello, a graduate of Musician's Institute and the Guitar
Institute of Technology, every week as he teaches not only the flash and 
style of playing guitar, but also the theory behind the music. As a member of
the northeast Pennsylvania group Totally Lost Cause, Charlie is in the process
of recording his third album, and he has also written his own teaching manual, 
 "The Expressive Guitarist", which he uses to teach from during "Guitar Shop".
In addition to the show, Charlie also gives private lessons and instructions in
both guitar and bass. To order a copy of his book, "The Expressive Guitarist",
call Charlie at (717) 963-1676, or write "The Expressive Guitarist, P.O. Box 4,
Scranton, Pa. 18509".  "Guitar Shop" may have started out as a five minute 
student project, but today it is TVM-37's most popular and talked about show.  












