<HTML>
<body background="/images/backgrnd.gif">
<B>Twilite with John Baldino</B><Br>
Do you find yourself bored with humdrum sitcom reruns? Are you sick of channel
surfing? well look now further--we have a show that will make you put down your
remote control once and for all (or at least for an hour.)<BR>
Tune into "Twilite" every Wednesday and Thursday night from 8:00-9:00p.m. for
the best of comedy, variety, and talk. Your host, John Baldino, will keep you
laughing while he banters with his sidekick, T.J.Foxx<BR>.
Each episode, "Twilite" features a monologue by Baldino, comedy with Foxx,
gossip reports by Adrea Oliver, Health & Fitness reports with Annette Hoyer
Bell, special guest interviews with Baldino, person-in-the-street interviews
with Tiffani Thompson, and mini-spy movies with Secret Agent Bob.<BR>
Baldino, exectutive producer/host, hopes to entertain his viewers while
showcasing local talent on "Twilite". He says, "Laughter is one of the best
sounds in the world, and laughing is one of the best feelings. I can make
people laugh, relax, and feel good. That's why I do 'Twilite'." 


</HTML>
