<H1>The Marywood Players present...</H1>
<H2>Children's Theatre</H2>
</Center>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<HR>
<H3>Children's Theatre returns to Marywood College.  This annual event is aimed
at the younger set (ages 3-10), and is delight for all.  This year's play is
"The Sorcerer's Apprentice" and will be performed from April 24-27 at the
Perfoming Arts Center - Main Stage.  April 24 at 10 am, April 25 and 26 at 10pm
and 1pm, and April 27 at 1pm.  If you have small children and want to keep them
entertained, bring them to the PAC.  For more information call
(717)348-6209.</H3>
