<Head>
<Title>Telecommunications</TITLE>
<body background="/images.backgrnd.gif">
<CENTER>
<H1>Telecommunications at Marywood</H1>
<H2>What's New</H2>
</CENTER>
<Head>
<Body>
<Hr>
<H3>Morning Madness<H3><BR>
<P>You mean you haven't heard???  VMFM is on in the morning now.  That's right,
every weekday morning between 7am and noon, you can hear WVMW-FM on the air
bringing you your morning dose of the usual chaos.  You also get news, sports,
and weather interspersed between it all, so that you can get to where you're going
without a hitch.  In the house, in the car, and in the workplace, let VMFM be
your companion.  Check out our <A href="schedule.html">schedule</A> to see
who's on at what time.  Maybe your favorite DJ has gone mad in the morning.

<P>This gile last updated on April 25, 1996<BR>
</Body>
</HTML>
