<BODY BGCOLOR="#B9E4BF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#AA00AA">

<A NAME="newstop"></A> <CENTER> 

<P> <FONT SIZE=-2>  &copy 1996 Microscopy-UK </FONT> </P> 

