<P>
<H2>Last Update: November 4, 1996</H2>
</P>

<FONT SIZE=+1>
<P>
It is incredibly exciting to look at something that most people have 
never seen, to enter a world few have glimpsed. I like to think of 
myself as a <FONT COLOR="DARKRED"><I>Micronaut</I></FONT>, 
similar to an astronaut, but instead of traveling into outer space, 
looking for alien life-forms, I travel into <I>micro-space</I> 
and find all sorts of alien-looking creatures. Astronauts use giant 
spaceships to propel themselves into space. My spaceship is a microscope 
and it takes me to places just as amazing and inspiring. 
</P>
<P>
There is <I>ALWAYS</I> something new and exciting to see. What I would 
like to do now is take you with me on many 
<FONT COLOR="DARKRED"><I>Micronautic Adventures</I></FONT>. 
You'll see just how interesting and fun these can be!
</P>
