Microscopix Photo-Library in the UK specialise in providing images of microscopic subjects for publishers, advertisers, and educationalists.
Their use of a Scanning Electron Microscope (SEM) enables incredible detailed images to be produced. Now you can
see them yourself. Microscopix has made a set of SEM images available for shareware use on your own PC. You can download this
set so that the unzipped images will be in your chosen format.<BR>

