</P>
<P>
We now have a separate section for vendors on Microscopy UK where we request a small charge for a link...we are an amateur non profit-making site and need to cover our overhead! We are also able to advertise your site more extensively in our new section.
</P>

<P>
We have had over 6000 unique readers and have over 10 000 Web pages accessed a month. We are one of the most active microscopy sites  on the Web and attract many readers from the professional microscopy and educational sector...it could be worth a link!  
Contact the <A HREF="mailto:mol@molcol.demon.co.uk">Microscopy UK Editor</A> for details.
</P>

