<a name="info">

<center><h5>About Micscape</center>

Micscape is a monthly publication from amateur microscopists. It is a free magazine for Internet users from Microscopy UK (a group of amateur microscopists in the UK) sponsored by several small businesses. The organisation itself is non profit-making although it publishes advertising for goods of interest to the microscopist and educationalist: all such commercial editorial is contained entirely in the <em>Professional Services</em> section of this site.<p>

All material in Micscape and in Microscopy UK is copyright of the contributors themselves. You are free to download and republish material for your own use only or for use in small projects in clubs or schools. No commercial re-publication is allowed without the written consent of the Editor. <a href="#top">Return to Top of Page</A><P>

</h5>
