<A NAME="qmc"></A> <P> <STRONG>Quekett Microscopical Club Annual
Exhibition Report </STRONG> </P> 



<P> Only a few hours ago at the time of writing, the doors
closed on one of the highlights of the UK amateur microscopist's
year ... the QMC Annual Exhibition in London.  <A
HREF="newsup2.html"> <STRONG>Read a special report</STRONG> </A>
by our roving reporter Maurice Smith (Microscopy UK Editor),
which also includes a link to the Club's suite of Web pages here
on Microscopy UK. The Club invites members from around the
world. </P>

