<H5>
<P>
Every effort is made to verify the Site addresses contained in this listing, <I>on a monthly basis</I>, but inevitably, some addresses will change without our knowledge. Please accept our apologies if you try to access a Site of interest to you and the link is no longer valid. If you wouldn't mind, we would appreciate you 
<A HREF="MAILTO: marlycain@aol.com">notifying us</A> if you find an invalid link in this listing. That will help us keep it accurate and up to date.
</P>
<P>
Please contact 
<A HREF="mailto:marlycain@aol.com">Marly Cain</A> 
if you would like a free link for your educational site to appear on this page. Contact 
<A HREF="mailto:mol@molcol.demon.co.uk"> Maurice Smith</A> 
if you require a link in our Vendors section and possibly additional advertising space for your commercial site.
