<p>

<a name="tech">
<UL><STRONG>Techniques</STRONG><BR>
<LI><A HREF="./articles/sem1.html">Specimen Preparation for SEM.</A> Scanning Electron Microscopy. Dec. 95
<li><A HREF="./articles/deepmic.html"><STRONG>Deep-field amateur microscopy</STRONG></A> May.96
<li><A HREF="./articles/poldw.html"><STRONG>Technicolour nature - using polarised light</STRONG></A> Jun.96  Novice
<li><A HREF="./articles/poldw2.html"><STRONG>Technicolour nature - crystals under polarised light</STRONG> </A>Part 2 of this series for Novices Jul. 96
