<STRONG>Editor's note</STRONG><BR>
The Micscape Editor thank William Ells for contributing this article. Note that Bill Ells has written six other articles on desmids, including an <A HREF="whatdesa.html"> introduction to the desmids</A> which can be found in our articles library in the Pond-life section.<P>

<center>
<H3>
<A HREF="../../index.html">Microscopy UK Front Page</A><br>
<A HREF="../indexmag.html">Micscape Magazine</A><br>
