<DOCNO>WT24-B18-224</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA060-000333-B004-8</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.microscopy-uk.org.uk:80/mag/articles/dingley1.html 194.88.132.107 19970115061016 text/html 9388
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
