<strong>Please Note:</strong> Microscopy UK is a non-commercial site offering a web presence to promote amateur microscopy

and related subjects. Our aim is a strong one which devours cash! The following professional services advertised here are 
the result of a selection process carried out by us to consider 'suitability'. Each of the advertisers 
have agreed to pay a small fee (to sponsor our site) or are providing help, information, or equipment
free of charge to help us maintain this site; this is done without any interference or control over the
running of our affairs. A lot of these small businesses are run by people who are themselves in love with amateur
microscopy. We run a strict policy of <strong>minimised</strong> advertising to ensure our site maintains a non-commercial status
which is enjoyable to read without being pestered to buy something.
<p>
Also included here are smaller services of interest to the amateur and small sales and wants which are advertised free
of any charge for non-commercial things. If you are an amateur looking for a special bit of kit or with something to trade
off or sell, then <a href="mailto:dave@diwalk.demon.co.uk"><STRONG>contact us</STRONG></A> to place your free advert.
