<DOCOLDNO>IA060-000333-B001-32</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.microscopy-uk.org.uk:80/mag/articles/ellsmuc.html 194.88.132.107 19970115055838 text/html 3999
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 06:04:40 GMT
