<p>
<font color="red" size=4>The IN-Visible Team
</font>
<p>
<font size=2>
Every Amateur 'Scoper', microscopist, human-being who contributes or has a go at 
looking a bit closer at their world and wants to share it with others. Tell us who you are and what aspect you are interesting in, and give us 
permission to include your details in our directory of Amateur Microscopists. More news on this shortly!
</font>
<br>
<br>
<CENTER><FONT COLOR="WHITE"><a href="mailto:mol@molcol.demon.co.uk">CENTRAL CONTACT POINT</a><FONT></CENTER>
<br>
<font color="red" size=2>
All files are &copy Microscopy-uk or &copy of the people contributing. Our collective works may be reused only for non-commercial publications 
in small clubs, and as part of school projects without permission. NO content should be republished on the web or electronically distributed without permission.
No commercial republication is allowed without permission from <A href="mailto:mol@molcol.demon.co.uk">The Microscopy-uk Co-ordinator</A>
