<H2>Brunel Microscopes Ltd.</h2>
<h3>On-line Catalogue of Microscopes and Accessories<BR><P>
1996 Edition</h3>
</center>
<hr>
<p>
<center>
<h3>Catalogue Index Page</h3>
</center>
<p>
We offer a wider range of microscopy items than included here in this electronic
catalogue. We hope these web pages will at least provide some help to you in reviewing 
our goods and selecting what you need. Please contact us if you can't see what you are
looking for or if you wish to check prices. All costs are quoted in pounds sterling and
are inclusive of Value Added Tax at 17.5 per cent. Additional charges will be added for 
packaging and shipping. The electronic catalogue layout and page references differs from
the paper one. Only a small sample of our equipment range is displayed here.
Please use equipment names and catalogue reference numbers starting with
in any enquiry to us regarding equipment details or price checks.
<p>
