<H1>BRUNEL MICROSCOPES</H1>
<PRE><H5>
Unit 12						From Europe Voice Tel: 0044-1249 462655  Fax: 0044-1249 701129
Enterprise Centre		      Rest of world:- contact your local operator for codes for the following
Bumpers Way      		       UK Telephone numbers. Voice Tel: 01249 701601 Fax: 01249 701129 
Bumpers Industrial Estate<BR>Chippenham, WILTS.               <a href="mailto:101353.3301@compuserve.com">Email us now.</A>
SN14 6QA
ENGLAND 
</h5> 
</pre>			
<p>
<center><strong><a href="bruncat.html"><img src="bruncat.gif"><br>
See our on-line catalogue!</A></strong></center>
<p>
<center><img src="../../rafile.gif"><br>
<strong><a href="brunel.ra">Hear a few words from us?</A></strong></center>
<p>
<HR>
<B> About Us</B><BR>
Brunel Microscopes Ltd have many years' professional experience in all aspects of microscopy and specimen preparation. We offer
a range of instruments ideally suited to the professional and amateur microscopist, as well as educational establishments and the student.<P>
<p>
<B>Contacting Us</B><BR>
We are a small company and pride ourselves on the personal service which this allows. We endeavour, as far as possible,
to have staff at one of our telephone numbers at all times. However, customer demonstrations and exhibitions does on occasion
mean that an 'answerphone' only is available. We apologise for this, and ask that whenever you contact us - if you do not 
receive personal assistance - you kindly leave your name, address, telephone / fax numbers, and/or email address. 
<P>
<B>Our Catalogue</B><BR>
We can send you a full paper-based catalogue (please contact us for details), or - <I>better still</I> - you can <B><A HREF="bruncat.html"> access our on-line catalogue</A></B> which 
contains a limited set of extractions from our full range. 
<P>
<B>Ordering</B><BR>
We can deliver to almost anywhere in the world. We accept several credit cards: VISA, ACCESS, and MASTERCARD. Although it is better for your personal
security if you don't send credit card numbers over the Internet (for the time being). You can order via email and fax or phone us your credit card
number to support your electronic order. This is a secure method. You can also pay for your order by cheque. A slight surcharge will be incurred if
your cheque is from outside the UK to cover bank charges. You can also order through the normal post by sending your order to the address above.

<B>If you wish to <A HREF="mailto:101353.3301@compuserve.com"> place an order now or simply obtain more information</A> about our services then we will be pleased
to hear from you.</B>

<P>

