<HEAD>
<TITLE>MICSCAPE - BRUNEL MICROSCOPES ON-LINE CATALOGUE  </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<center>
<h3>BRUNEL MICROSCOPES LTD<BR>
On-line Catalogue of Microscopes and Accessories<BR><P>
Page 3</h3>
</center>
<hr>
<h3>WEDMORE SP SERIES MICROSCOPES <br>
 Price range: 79.00 to 158.00 UK Pounds.</H3>
<IMG SRC="brun3i1.gif" alt="" align=left hspace=12>
The Wedmore series microscopes are a range of high quality, high performance
instruments available exclusively from Brunel Microscopes. The robost design of these
instruments is particularly suited to the rigours of educational establishments and the 
dedicated amateur naturalist. The excellent optical performance is exceptional for a 
microscope in this price range.
<p>
The Wedmore range is designed to give a <b>modular approach</b> to microscopy, offering
a number of specifications which can therefore be <b>matched to budgets</b> and optical
requirements.
<p>
<br>
<br>
<b>Abbe Condenser and Iris Diaphragm</b><br>
Irrespective of model, all Wedmore SP microscopes are equipped with a full substage 
Abbe condenser (N.A. 1.2), with iris diaphragm, filter carrier and full rack and pinion 
adjustment. The full size microscope stands are of a suitable die-cast construction, finished
in grey enamel and may be inclined for convenient operation.
<p>
<b>The Price Beater!</b><br>
The economic price of the Wedmore range allows the purchase of a full sized <b>professional</b>
microscope, incorporating <b>RMS standard thread acromatic objectives</b>, with full sub-stage 
condenser, for little more than the cost of sub-standard microscopes available. Now there is no
excuse for buying toy instruments when this quality instrument with glass optics can offer high
quality study and durable service at low prices.
<p>
<i><b>Looking for a starter instrument..? Then this is the scope for you!</b></i><br>
<h3>Just look at the specification:-</h3>
Quadruple objective turret, separate coarse and fine focus controls, square specimen stage
with slide clips, which can also accomodate a mechanical specimen driver, illumination by mirror and 
gimbal, which can be replaced by a substage 240v, 12 Watt lamp unit which provides optimum illumination 
at all magnifications.
<p>
<br>
<p>
<b>The wide range of accessories</b> include: measuring equipment, photography and drawing attachments, together
with a list which enables the basic unit <b>(SP01)</b> to be fully upgraded to the <b>(SP14)</b> on a pricemeal basis.
<i>Alternatively,</i> the Wedmore can be purchased with a complete specification <b>(detailed below)</b> at a price
advantage. The additional items available with the specification of each successive model are highlighted in bold
type. Remember, all models have coarse and fine focus and fully adjustable Abbe condenser with iris diaphragm as standard,
and may be fitted with a safety stop.
<p>

<center><h3>WEDMORE SP SERIES ACCESSORIES</h3></center>
<b>Using the SP01 as the basic unit, any individual specification may be assembled from this list of accessories:-</b>

<pre>
   Mechanical stage                (BM780) - 23.00 UK Pounds
   Wooden Case                     (BM792) -  8.00 UK Pounds
   Eyepiece micrometer             (BM787) - 12.00 UK Pounds
   Spare bulb                      (BM782) -  3.00 UK Pounds
   Substage lamp                   (BM781) - 25.00 UK Pounds
   Polariser/analyser              (BM785) - 14.00 UK Pounds
   Stage micrometer                (BM945) - 16.00 UK Pounds
   x4 objective                    (BM789) - 15.00 UK Pounds
   x10 widefield eyepiece          (BM791) - 19.00 UK Pounds
   x10 objective                   (BM797) - 14.00 UK Pounds
   x16 eyepiece                    (BM806) - 14.00 UK Pounds
   x40 objective                   (BM799) - 24.00 UK Pounds
   x100 oil objective              (BM798) - 28.00 UK Pounds
   Photomicrography attachment     (BM783) - 21.00 UK Pounds
   T2 ring state camera make       (BM940) -  9.00 UK Pounds
   Dark field condenser            (BM803) - No Stock!
   Focus Stop                      (BM805) - Email us for price.
   Drawing Attachment              (BML003)- 19.00 UK Pounds
   Stereo Adaptor                  (BML004)- 11.00 UK Pounds
</pre>
<p>
<h3>Complete Specifications for a few models in the range:-</h3>
<b>SP01</b> <i>magnification range x100 - x400</i> <b>Price: 79.00 UK Pounds</b>
<pre>
   Objectives   x10, x40
   Eyepieces    x10
   Stage clips
</pre>
<p>
<b>SP03</b> <i>magnification range x50 - x500</i> <b>Price: 91.00 UK Pounds</b>
<pre>
   Objectives   x10, x40
