to disk. You will find it useful.
<h3>Microscopy UK: Professional Services</h3>
<h3>Download *FREE* Molcol Software from the Internet</h3>
</CENTER>
<HR SIZE=4>



<center><H3>
All software is available from this page. Make sure you read down it
carefully. A list of point and shoot links is at the bottom of the page!
Did you read the help file first..? <a href="softmol.html">No!</A> / <a href="#down">Yes!</A>
</H3></center>




<a name="down">
All of Molcol's Software can be downloaded from Simtel Mirror Sites.
The following files are available. You might like to take a note
of them before accessing the Simtel Sites. Read the file information
below then <a href="#list">Go get the software</A><br>
================================================================
<pre>
Info files
-----------
00_index.txt    (internal-gopher-text)			Size= 1 Kb
mpc-diz.zip	(Info on each file in the directory)	Size= 5 Kb


Core Software
-------------
*Use need both of these: Part 1 & 2!

ms3part1.zip	:	Microscope for the PC Part 1	size: 1330 Kb
ms3part2.zip	:	Microscope for the PC Part 2	size: 1415 Kb


A speed bug fix
---------------
bugfix30.zip	:	If the core software runs too fast or too slow
                        on your PC in DOS or Windows.   Size= 9 Kb 


Demo only 
----------
mic_demo.zip	:	Microscope DEMO only. 		Size= 676 Kb
*You can't use slidesets with this module. 


Shareware Slidesets
--------------------
ms_set2.zip	:	Microscope SLIDESETS Pack 2	Size= 1382 Kb
ms_set3.zip	:	Microscope SLIDESETS Pack 3	Size=  970 Kb
ms_set4.zip	:	Microscope SLIDESETS Pack 4	Size= 1295 Kb
ms_set5.zip	:	Microscope SLIDESETS Pack 5	Size= 1224 Kb
ms_set6.zip	:	Microscope SLIDESETS Pack 6	Size= 1413 Kb
ms_set7.zip	:	Microscope SEM SLIDESETS Pack 7 Size= 1082 Kb
*All the above need Part1 & Part2 of the core software!

Wallpapers for Windows
------------------------
micwall1.zip	:	Microscope WALLPAPERS Pack 1	Size= 1341 Kb
micwall2.zip	:	Microscope WALLPAPERS Pack 2	Size= 1399 Kb
freepics.zip	:	Free Pictures			Size=  589 Kb

* All these three contain the same images
sem_bmp.zip	:	SEM images in BMP format	Size= 1062 Kb
sem_gif.zip	:	SEM images in GIF format	Size= 1299 Kb
sem_jpg.zip	:	SEM images in JPG format	Size=  376 Kb

