<h3>
Various methods of accessing SimTel files
Revised: Mar. 17, 1996 
</h3>
<pre>
SimTel, the Coast to Coast Software Repository (tm), is located on
SimTel.Coast.NET, a host that (for security reasons) does not allow public 
access by ftp users, however its files are available by anonymous
ftp in directories:-
		 /SimTel/msdos
		 /SimTel/win3
		 /SimTel/win95
                 /SimTel/nt 
		 /SimTel/vendors 

on SimTel's primary mirror site:-   <strong> FTP.Coast.NET </strong>

and from the secondary mirror sites below.

The Simtel directory structure includes a dedicated directory for 
Microscopy Software. The following links below should take you
straight to a Simtel Mirror Site near you and right into the
microscopy directory, where you will be able to see a list of
Molcol Software's files and download the ones you want to try out!
</pre>
<br>
<hr>
<a name="list">
<p>
<center><h3>Go get the Software</h3></center>
<h4>
If any link below fails or is too slow,  pick another one from the 
list below. Simply find the row with a location closet to where you live and
then click on the entry in the <em>Go There</em> column. If you want 
to exit your browser and try using your ftp software directly, you need
to combine the Name of the 'Simtel Mirror Site' with the 'Go There' directory-
filename to form an FTP address. For example, from the first entry in the table:-
<p>
<center><strong> ftp to: </strong> archie.au/micros/pc/SimTel/msdos/microscp/</center>
<p>
<em>There should be no need to do this:</em> just use the comprehensive <em>Live
Links</em> below to grab the software! Be patient during the connection
time as initial delays may be caused as the server searches for the correct
directory.

</h4>

