<p>
   
There are other sites (more than 65, and growing) that mirror SimTel's
collections.  Many serve only their own country or region and do not
wish to receive International traffic.  At their request they are not
listed above.
<p>
SimTel files may obtained by e-mail from various ftp-mail servers
or through the BITNET/EARN file servers.  For details send e-mail
to listserv@SimTel.Coast.NET with this command in the body of the
message:  get simtel-mailserver.info
<p>
Gopher users can access SimTel files through Gopher.Oakland.Edu
<p>
CD-ROM copies of the SimTel collections are available from Coast to Coast
Telecommunications, Inc., 5850 Dixie Highway Clarkston, MI 48346, U.S.A.,
telephone (800) 900-9960 or (810) 623-6700, or FAX (810) 623-1469.  
These CD-ROMs are unabridged copies, which is not true of CD-ROMs sold by 
some other vendors which offer only portions of the collections.  For 
information send e-mail to cdrom@Mail.Coast.NET. To order send e-mail to 
order@Mail.Coast.NET. 
<p>
SimTel's primary source of support comes from direct sales of CD-ROMs
sold by Coast to Coast Telecommuncations, Inc. (CCT).  The best way you
can help SimTel to expand and improve its services to you is to tell
friends and business contacts about our CD-ROMs, and to encourage them
to purchase direct from CCT instead of other CD-ROM vendors.
