<p>
<h3>About our games</h3>
These games are either FREEWARE or SHAREWARE as indicated on this page. 
<em>Freeware</em> is FREE for good! <em>Shareware</em> is free-trial only. There is a difference!
All games can be run from Windows 3.1 up to Windows95. They contain sound and music which can be 
turned off if you want a quiet life. Each game has its own help file. They are FUN games designed to keep your kids amused 
and possibly you too in your lunchbreak at work. If the boss comes along, hit 
F5 (the panic key) and the game will immediately disappear from your screen until
you hit F5 again. See how thoughtful we are?!

