<center>
<br>
<h4>"You are not alone!"<br>
This page has been visited 3420x <br> by people around the world since <br>
April 18th 1996
</h4>
</center>


<UL>
<h4>
Welcome to Microscopy UK's Fractal Image Gallery.
Here you can get larger, higher quality images, which
can be zoomed to fill your entire screen!<p>

The images are stored in the new "fractal image format"
(*.fif files). An image file size is small compared to its
original size. You need a "plug-in" or "helper app" depending
on which browser you use. Click on the button at the top of this
page to go and get your <em>*FREE*</em> Fractal Image Viewer.

We change out the entire gallery periodically. This new one was started
on August 20th 1996. We will be adding additional images over the coming weeks.


</h4>
</UL>
<br>
<br>
<a name="sel">
<UL>
<center>
<h3>Left-click on the associated tag to see an image from the fractal
gallery or right-click on the tag to save the image to disk</h3>
<strong>(More Images will be added shortly)</strong>
</center>
</UL>


