<a name="links">
<center><h1>School Link</h1></center>
Would you like to link to other schools? Run projects together? Check results? Compare results..? 
Then drop us a line at <a href="mailto:mol@molcol.demon.co.uk">microscopy-uk School's Link</A>
and we will link you in here!
<P>
