how it all worked and it fell over. My colleague (who is a professional PC support person) is still trying to get Win95 working again. I guess, since Win95 is meant to be a really friendly user-interface, it's easy! If you know how to set up Micmovie in Win95, be a friend for life and <A href="mailto:mol@molcol.demon.co.uk">let me know</A> please.<p><center><h3>Ah-ha! A friend is made:-</h3></center><strong>Gord Burton wrote in to say...</strong>
