<DOCNO>WT24-B18-281</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA060-000332-B010-264</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.microscopy-uk.org.uk:80/mag/articles/size.html 194.88.132.107 19970115053001 text/html 9293
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 05:36:03 GMT
