<HEAD>
<TITLE>Microscopy UK / MICSCAPE - 3D Stereo Microscopy : Insects</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#000000" text="#00ff00">

<a name="top">

<P>
<center><h1>3D Ant drinking honey</h1></center>
<p>

<center><IMG SRC="3dhoney.jpg"></center>
<h4>
You should have no problems seeing the effect on this image of an Ant drinking
a tiny drop of honey. I put down the drop to tempt the ant to pose long enough for me to 
film it. The image was 'sampled' from the resulting video film and then turned into
a hologram using <a href="3dAds.html"> <STRONG>DOUBLE VISION</STRONG></A> software.

</h4>
<p>
